---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site.mjs';
---
<Base title="Shipping & Returns" description="How Tantu Kala ships handmade orders, and our returns & refund policy.">
  <div class="wrap py-10 max-w-2xl prose-tk">
    <h1 class="text-4xl">Shipping & Returns</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/60">
      Please review this before ordering. <em>Edit the bracketed parts to match your real policy.</em>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Payment</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-ink/80">
      We accept secure <strong>UPI</strong> payment on this website. After you place an order you'll
      get an order number and a UPI payment option (tap-to-pay on mobile, scan-QR on desktop).
      We verify your payment against your order number before we dispatch.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Shipping</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-ink/80">
      We ship across India. <em>[State your courier, dispatch time, and delivery estimate — e.g.
      "Orders are dispatched within 2–4 days; delivery in 3–7 days depending on location."]</em>
      For Raksha Bandhan, order by <strong>{new Date(SITE.orderCutoffISO).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long' })}</strong>
      to receive in time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Returns & Refunds</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-ink/80">
      Every piece is <strong>handmade to order</strong>, so we're unable to accept returns for
      change of mind. If your order arrives <strong>damaged or incorrect</strong>, message us within
      <em>[48 hours]</em> with a photo and we'll replace it or refund you. <em>[State how refunds are
      issued and the timeline.]</em>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Handmade note</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-ink/80">
      Because each rakhi is crocheted by hand, small variations in colour and size are natural and
      not considered defects.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-ink/80">
      This site takes no payment data and stores nothing on your device except your cart. The
      delivery details you enter at checkout are used only to process and ship your order.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 card p-5 bg-sand">
      <p class="text-sm text-ink/70">
        Questions? Message us on
        <a href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.whatsapp}`} class="text-henna font-semibold underline">WhatsApp</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
